name: XV Anniversary Gift Box (Alpha)
description: The XV Anniversary Gift Box was created by the Society of Conscious Thought to commemorate 15 years of Capsuleers in New Eden. This box contains the following: 1x Apotheosis 1x Wings of Victory Firework 1x Men's Capsuleer Elite XV T-Shirt 1x Men's Capsuleer Elite XV Cap 1x Women's Capsuleer Elite XV T-Shirt 1x Women's Capsuleer Elite XV Cap 1x Apotheosis Capsuleer Elite XV SKIN 1x Capsule Capsuleer Elite XV SKIN
